Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:06.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱音  轮盘选择了你和让治
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:10.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢解放之日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:50.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  纱音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:54.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以看出你的嘴边充满着留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让让治教你女人的快感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:03.28,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为连初夜都没经历就要被杀死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满是留恋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:09.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:33.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差点忘了  你也是金藏的优秀家具啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:38.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让嘉音君的尸体消失还损害了他的名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:44.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  纱音  你在生这个气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:46.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再让你们见一次面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很愉快吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:58.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生离死别的人们再次相会无论何时都是很愉快的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:02.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  嘉音  陪他们玩玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:08.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一而再再而三地玷污死者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:09.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:17.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让治  请不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想移动中心轴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.78,0:03:30.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可真令人惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:35.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  灵镜借给你力量了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:38.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说家具真可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:43.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就像不小心脚趾头撞到了衣柜一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:50.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是家具  并且我认为此刻的你非常可悲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:51.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:54.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相爱的两人不可能没有留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:04:00.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们却没有你所期待的一点点留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还讲道理  你这家具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:07.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于相爱的两人来说身体的交融一定有其意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:11.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那与你所说的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.45,0:04:12.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它赋有神圣的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:20.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和让治发誓永远相爱  作为证明而接受了戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:22.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经完成了永恒的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我已无任何留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:29.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说漂亮话  你这家具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:36.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会失望的  你只要看过一次身后那眼镜男的肮脏欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.34,0:04:40.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊算了  少废话  你这家具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:44.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧  你这破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:53.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:01.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让治  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.65,0:05:04.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  纱音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:12.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了我挺身而出
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:14.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是这样我就很高兴了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让治  我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:21.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:26.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后请让我听你说爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:31.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  纱代  我永远都…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:34.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你听吗  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楼座夫人  我是源次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:58.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.78,0:06:02.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现南条医生和熊泽的尸体了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:06.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  现在就去确认
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:13.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是被日本刀之类的东西砍了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第七夜  剜膝杀之」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第八夜  剜足杀之」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:28.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  这样的话就少了第四到第六夜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源次先生  让治哥他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:37.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们说要去夏妃夫人的房间里找东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:39.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是两三小时之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:45.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我们也去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请开门
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:01.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门被锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战人君  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:07.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:19.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让治哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:31.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纱音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战人君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:36.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察到来之前不能乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这果然是第四到第六夜的再现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:46.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来直到第八夜为止就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九夜是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:56.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「第九夜  魔女复苏  无人生还」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:08:02.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我们将要死去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.10,0:08:05.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…  别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:08.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  源次先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送到这里就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.02,0:08:15.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有事请随时吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:20.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下竟然置源次先生于不顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,楼座伯母
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.93,0:08:41.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:50.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:56.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K200\b1\1c&H804000&\2a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}碑文之谜进展如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K200\b1\1c&H804000&\2a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}时限马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:04.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\K240\b1\1c&H804000&\2a&HFF&\3a&HFF&\4a&HFF&}第九夜即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战人  那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.22,0:09:10.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚  你到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:12.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:16.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:19.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战人君  我断定你是狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:20.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:22.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我会被怀疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.15,0:09:25.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你之外没人会放下这封信了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:29.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要无法证明你的清白你就是狼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:33.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  要说我可疑的话你也很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:36.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让我注意到偷偷地放下了信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反过来也可以怀疑你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:41.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是狼早就开枪射杀你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不算理由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:47.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  楼座伯母一开始就很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:49.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参加亲族会议的大人们被杀了六人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:52.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只有楼座伯母不在那礼拜堂里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.70,0:09:58.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是伯母把老爸他们召集到那里并杀害了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就全都能说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:11.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不坏  战人和妈妈都不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:15.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是魔女用魔法干的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:24.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情我已经受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:28.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶手是魔女  是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  现身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:39.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我们宣布全都是自己用魔法干的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:44.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝亚特丽切！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.24,0:10:53.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能再次看见你的微笑  我就死而无憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我思慕你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.35,0:11:02.96,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少让我向你道一声歉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.00,0:11:05.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.12,0:11:07.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.88,0:11:18.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝亚特丽切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:30.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  门没锁  要进来就进来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.76,0:11:33.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是源次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.37,0:11:35.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战人少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:38.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为是时候让您知道一切了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:44.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请直接听馆主大人他们向您说明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:46.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:51.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馆主大人  我把他带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:58.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:17.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来的好  右代宫战人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:18.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:23.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有事要问我不是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.65,0:12:28.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往黄金乡的大门即将开启
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前你要问多少问题我都会回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会发生这样的事件？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密室的钥匙呢？魔女的真面目呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:41.54,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把我叫到这里来？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都给我解释清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:50.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  只是有一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:55.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你能接受我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:59.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那时就给我跪下  亲吻我的靴尖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:05.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了让你屈服才把你叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要能让我接受的话吻靴子什么的叫我做什么我都做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:17.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那先从哪个问题开始回答呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会全部回答的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:43.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最起码拿走一条
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:48.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就能见到贝亚特丽切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝亚特丽切在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:53.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黄金乡就能见到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧？赶快现身吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.27,0:14:04.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝亚特丽切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.07,0:14:11.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜已完成了复苏的我们黄金乡的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝亚特丽切卿到场
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:32.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:36.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  贝伦卡斯特尔卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:39.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临  你还喜欢我的家具吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.86,0:14:41.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不得的趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.09,0:14:49.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜诸位为我欢聚一堂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:51.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完结和起始的指针将重合于一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:55.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:57.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.20,0:15:01.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启黄金之门！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:16.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝亚特丽切  现在就让我去黄金乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.35,0:15:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我跪下  表示你的敬意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.70,0:15:38.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我贴紧地面  显露你的卑微吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚  快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:02.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:04.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.59,0:16:08.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我眼前你们敢碰真里亚一根手指头试试
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:12.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你们认识到  原来身处的地狱还根本算不上地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚  帮忙装弹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会装
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你们见识见识
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金之梦是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.62,0:16:31.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  子弹装好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:39.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚  即使妈妈这么坏  还愿意和妈妈在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.53,0:16:41.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和妈妈在一起最好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:44.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真里亚的  唯一的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:48.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金什么的根本就用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:51.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要牵着你的手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:55.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一个多么愚蠢的妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:16:59.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚  一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:02.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:04.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妈妈永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:20.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所期望的东西我都可以给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为给你那超强运气的奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的痛楚是来自于兄弟姐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:35.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就送给你报复他们的喜悦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.86,0:17:43.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饮食占人们快乐中的很大一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们开始美食之宴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:51.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这杯是餐前酒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:54.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要取名的话就是血腥藏臼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:57.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是把那个一直耀武扬威的藏臼大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:18:02.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狠狠地拧干之后榨出来的鲜血之酒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:12.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这盘是用正当时下的蔬菜调配而成的舌片色拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.81,0:18:16.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是用你在九岁生日时就想咬碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:20.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绘羽的舌头所制作的你期望已久的色拉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:23.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一盘是用一直出卖你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:27.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留弗夫的脸皮包的鲈鱼派
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:32.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜点是你一直假装疼爱的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:42.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  真里亚的存在是不是一个障碍？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:48.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈往家里面带男人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:52.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和男人在外面过夜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:55.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚总是给你添麻烦  制造障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.43,0:18:58.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我生下来  真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把真里亚吃了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:06.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚为了妈妈变成了美味的烤苹果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:11.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己女儿做成的烤苹果  真是最棒的甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:13.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养育了这么一个好吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是最厉害的母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右代宫楼座
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:26.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你对我的款待还满意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:29.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就承认我的存在吧  承认我是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右代宫楼座  承认贝亚特丽切是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:41.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢耍小聪明的战人已经屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:42.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's  perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.88,0:19:46.02,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看似挺好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也为我露一手  把你的奶子切成肉片做个三明治给我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:52.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:54.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战…战人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:58.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是成为家具连灵魂都已经屈服了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:02.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚  要说把自己吃掉之类的话还早了十年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:05.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  过了十年一定要跟我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.82,0:20:06.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:09.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜  约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.29,0:20:10.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是决不能屈服的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:15.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了楼座伯母坚持到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再一次有了战斗的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:20.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种  我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受你的挑战  右代宫战人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.22,0:20:26.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事就否定我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:28.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.76,0:20:30.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.01,0:20:38.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  这一盘的游戏玩的开心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.22,0:20:41.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一边倒的单方面游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:42.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「贝伦卡斯特尔卿没有胜算」是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.33,0:20:47.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜算？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:50.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用装糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并不是旁观者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我说对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.31,0:21:03.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.19,0:21:07.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然能获得和那个最强的魔女贝伦卡斯特尔卿对战的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:11.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了  贝伦卡斯特尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:14.43,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也闲得慌呢  拉姆达
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自把别人的名字省略成拉姆达啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.06,0:21:22.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我告诉她你正和我对立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:26.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆达德尔塔卿就说她要站到和你对立的位置上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:29.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在记仇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:34.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡是和你作对的人不论是谁我都视为同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.18,0:21:36.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱怎么样就怎么样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然露馅了我也干脆认真来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.60,0:21:42.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就下盘游戏见吧

Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:20.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真里亚  真里亚  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:22.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我这个坏妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:24.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再打你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:28.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这封信…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:33.33,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秋叶原站不认识的哥哥给的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.80,0:23:36.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右代宫楼座小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:40.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被动画中你的表现一箭穿心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:46.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨人厌的非正常表现  真的很给力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.97,0:23:51.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想被你的右脚践踏  嘿  嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.41,0:23:54.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体观众奉上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.38,0:23:59.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  castling
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:04.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:10.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想变得像南瓜糖一样粉碎的家伙们  尽管上前



